Text.SourceString: Ah, goomgoom!
A hooman can see <NPCName>Groo</>.
Wheeee! <NPCName>Groo</> can run again.
Hooman! Go run too! Wheeeee!
<NPCName>Groo</> don't remember how to things after stuck for so long.
Aaah... Wind.
Giants can help you.//Giants grow food too.
Giants the best food grower. Hooman lose.//Heh heh heh!
<NPCName>Groo</> collects food from forest.//Hooman too, goom?
Goddess food the best!//Better than Giant's.
Hooman done talking to <NPCName>Groo</>? I want to run and pick fruit!
I don't sleep.//<NPCName>Groo</> strong.
<NPCName>Groo</> fix tool.//The best. Heh heh heh!
Hooman, thank for saving <NPCName>Groo</>. Now <NPCName>Groo</> is not stone anymore!
Giants like town. Many yummy food.
Giants hate town. Many bouncy hooman.
<NPCName>Grog</> is too slow! But <NPCName>Grog</> is friend, even when sooooo slooooow.
<NPCName>Groo</> ask <NPCName>Gong</> to run but <NPCName>Gong</> says too tired.//<NPCName>Gong</> old. Heh heh heh!
Hooman want better tool? <NPCName>Groo</> can help!//But only two. Not allowed more.
Why Hooman stop <NPCName>Groo</>? <NPCName>Groo</> busy!
Giants work better together.//If Hooman want better tool, save more Giants.
Ah, goom, Hooman. Yes.
Everything so wet!//Last time <NPCName>Groo</> fall and hit head...
<NPCName>GONG</> SKY LEAK TOO MUCH AGAIN! ARGH!
Giants need fire... Cold outside.//Hm, now <NPCName>Groo</> sad...
Don't remember anything from stone age...//<NPCName>Groo</> got stoned and slept.
Hooman go to cavern, yes? Where <NPCName>Groo</> was stone?//Why?! It scary!
<NPCName>Groo</> likes to run through the leaves. Wheeeee!//Wind the best! Better than water. Heh heh heh!
Snowpeople look like Giants sometimes.//Only the good ones.
Bored! <NPCName>Groo</> just want to run in the forest.//Doing useless stuff like Hooman. I want.
<NPCName>Gong</> is fast sometimes! Like the wind.//But only sometimes. Most times, <NPCName>Groo</> is faster. Like the wind. Woosh!
<NPCName>Groo</> is feeling slow today...//It must be what Hooman feel all time.
Storm so fast! Maybe one day <NPCName>Groo</> can be as fast as storm.
Why can Hooman see Giants? Other hooman in hooman village can't.//Strange it is...
Why Hooman look like that? So tall. Eyes so big and strange...
<NPCName>Groo</> not like village when rain like this. Too slippy!
<NPCName>Groo</> not like village when rain like this. Too slippy!
<NPCName>Groo</> not like village when snow like this. Too slippy!
<NPCName>Groo</> tired today. Maybe go outside later.
Sun is like eye, yes? Watching us all during the day.
So loud outside!
White fluffy cold, white fluffy cold~
So much nice nice fruit now! Forest is rich. Sprouting Season here!//Giants grow seeds in forest too for animal friends.
Sometimes <NPCName>Groo</> see small hooman eating lot of colorful things on stick. Look so nice and yum yum!//Small hooman can see Giants. Yes.
<NPCName>Groo</> a little sad leaves are falling but <NPCName>Groo</> know leaves will be back in Sprouting Season.
Time to see pretty flowers. Busy time for Giants.
Hooman always get together near lake in Sprouting Season.//Food smells yummy! Giants want to join.
Forest so full again! Giants home.//Thank you, Hooman.
So many new sprouts this Sprouting Season. Nice to see.//It make wind smell yummy.
Maybe <NPCName>Groo</> not zoom so much now. Slippy ice.
